    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>javascript</code> to do so. Have a look as follows:</p>\n\n<pre><code>function addValue(value) {\n document.form.input.value=value;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You have to set this <code>javascript</code> source code in a <code>javascript</code> section (it is placed usually at the head code).</p>\n\n<p>In order to invoke that code, you should tell 'button' where the function is defined:</p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;input type=\"button\" name=\"one\" value=\"1\" onClick='addValue(1)'&gt;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And that's all.</p>\n"
  } ],
